						Seipso contentus, non [l]editur ab alijs.
					</marginalia_text>
				</position>
			</language>
			<translation>
				He who is not offended by others is content with himself.
			</translation>
		</marginalia>
		<marginalia hand="Italian">
			<language ident="LA">
				<position place="intext" book_orientation="0">
					<marginalia_text>
						( Omnia Eutrapelo dulcia:
						( nihil amarum.
					</marginalia_text>
					<person name="Eutrapelus"/>
				</position>
			</language>
			<translation>
				For Eutrapelus, all things are sweet, nothing is bitter.
			</translation>
		</marginalia>
		<marginalia hand="Italian">
			<language ident="EN">
				<position place="intext" book_orientation="0">
					<marginalia_text>
						( Heauen vpon Earth. )
					</marginalia_text>
				</position>
			</language>
